<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Flyobo Travel Account</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 32px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4B0082, #00b4d8);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 36px 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        .header span {
            color: #FFD700;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 8px 0 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 36px 24px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .otp-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }
        .otp-code {
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 6px;
            color: #4B0082;
            background: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 2px dashed #4B0082;
        }
        .cta-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4B0082;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 36px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(75, 0, 130, 0.3);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .cta-btn:hover {
            background-color: #3a0075;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .warning {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 16px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #777;
            margin-top: 32px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .otp-code {
                font-size: 28px;
                padding: 12px 24px;
                letter-spacing: 4px;
            }
            .cta-btn {
                padding: 12px 24px;
                font-size: 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to <span>Flyobo Travel</span>!</h1>
            <p>Let's get your account verified.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
            <p>To complete your registration and secure your account, please use the One-Time Password (OTP) below:</p>
            
            <div class="otp-container">
                <span class="otp-code"><%= otp %></span>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align:center;">
                <a href="https://flyobo.com/verify?email=<%= encodeURIComponent(email) %>&otp=<%= otp %>" class="cta-btn">Verify Account</a>
            </div>

            <p class="warning">⚠️ This OTP is valid for <strong>10 minutes</strong>. Please do not share it with anyone.</p>

            <p>If you need help, feel free to reply to this email or contact our support team.</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 32px;">With gratitude,<br/><strong>The Flyobo Travel Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Flyobo Travel. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
